      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Your Application for the Senior Dev Role\n\nDear Marcus,\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to take a moment to thank you for the time and effort you invested in the interview process for the Senior Dev role here in Austin. Your enthusiasm and technical prowess were truly impressive, and we were delighted to learn about your experience and passion for development.\n\nAfter careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with another candidate who has a bit more experience with our specific cloud architecture. This decision was not easy, as we were impressed by your skills and potential. However, we believe that this particular candidate's experience aligns more closely with our current needs.\n\nWe truly appreciate your interest in joining our team and wish you the best in your future endeavors. We hope you will keep an eye on our careers page for future opportunities that may be a better fit for your skills and experience.\n\nThank you once again for your time and effort.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
