      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that's a good start. Could you make it sound a little less \"template-y\"? Specifically, maybe add a sentence or two acknowledging how much we enjoyed the conversation with him, and keep that empathetic tone, but don't let it get too soft—we don't want him thinking there's a chance for this specific role if he appeals it. Just a slightly more personal touch while staying strictly professional.",
      "source": "evaluator"
